        <scopecontent>
          <head>Scope and Contents</head>
          <p>This series includes transfer and dismission correspondence, meeting minutes, financial
            reports, committee and pastor's reports, and activity records of clubs and auxiliary
            groups. Notable documents include the "List of Strays" notebook recording farm animals
            escaping their pens in the immediate area, wills and bequests of some church members,
            and documentation of the church's closure.</p>
        </scopecontent>
